# Go: the canonical generated module (root go.mod + recursive .go) IS tracked as a reviewed derived
# artifact (verified byte-exact against the pristine Buildx layer by the pre-commit staged-index check), so
# *.go is NOT ignored.  Ignore ONLY this repository's transient local control/crash residue: the exact root
# .fido/ control dir and any abandoned reserved sibling temps.  A NESTED .fido is an emission ERROR and is
# deliberately NOT ignored (it must stay visible if it ever appears).
/.fido/
**/*.fido-tmp-v1
/fido
*.test
*.out
vendor/

# Plugin / sink build artifacts (generated in the build, never tracked).
/sink_test
*.cmi
*.cmo
*.cmx
*.cmxs
*.o

# Environment
.env

# Rocq build artifacts — .v sources are checked in, these are not
*.glob
*.vo
*.vok
*.vos
*.vio
*.aux
.*.aux
.lia.cache
.nia.cache
.coq-native/
_build/
